casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Alex CONSTANTOPES.
No. D-2961.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 17, 2017.
Alex Constantopes, of Jackson Heights, New York, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
